               </msIdentifier>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Image of the Savior of the world (images 1-21). Short version of the Five Pillars. Mystery of the Trinity (images 21-24), Mystery of the Incarnation (images 24-25), Mystery of Baptism (images 25-26). Mystery of Communion (images 26-29). Mystery of the Resurrection (images 29-32). Teachings of the Fathers (images 32-40). Concluding note on the time of completion of the copying. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
